NT_JOB EBFSBPI_PASS1
   AGENT APPPLS01PAKR
   USER bsprintuser
   CMDNAME E:\APPS\FIRESTONE_BUILDING_PRODUCTS\START\+
   BUILDINGPRODUCTS_PASS_1.BAT
